{"id": 2103, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都为自己创造过哪些（不必要的）购物欲？", "description": "回想一下自己产生购物欲的时刻，是哪些微妙的原因让你觉得“本来也没想买啥新东西，但……就是此刻，不买不行了！”（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 6936, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180103123832gr60AvwXZIKan9hG.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-03T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3532, "title": "你都为自己创造过哪些（不必要的）购物欲？", "content": "你都为自己创造过哪些（不必要的）购物欲？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 257677, "content": "逛商城/淘宝特价区，鬼使神差下单用不着的东西 ", "image": "img/option/option/20180103115247ot28s1Di4V9v6ny0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257679, "content": "成套产品/福袋里就有一件想要的，买！其他都当赠品", "image": "img/option/option/20180103115307wmp39cfDYbRSFhME.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257681, "content": "陪朋友逛街，自己试穿/试用之后心（冲）动消费", "image": "img/option/option/201801031159299hsmoKn0kqidWTce.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257685, "content": "要出席重要场合，现有的鞋子衣服包没有一样顺眼 ", "image": "img/option/option/20180103115911RdonjhveFXqKfrbW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257686, "content": "换季时点开“保暖/消夏神器”推荐贴，看完下了好几单", "image": "img/option/option/20180103120429Frgk2CS8c7xGnB41.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257687, "content": "给自己定了购物周期，隔段时间就觉得必须得买点啥", "image": "img/option/option/20180103115959SYwnVghbBc0OTEF8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257689, "content": "觉得划算而充卡办会员，“以后应该都赚得回来吧” ", "image": "img/option/option/20180103120333AabQGivJszC289fY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257690, "content": "这东西虽然不实用，但先买回来呗大不了当礼物送人", "image": "img/option/option/20180103120014mFlfGL5sjAMqu4KZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 257691, "content": "被“行家”“速成”“年薪五十万”蛊惑，买知识付费产品", "image": "img/option/option/20180103120621QSRNzZBuUD0XHvtL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}